These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, artichoke
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, motorbike
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | peach   | artichoke   |
| Transport   | motorbike | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, handball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   |
| Sport      | handball | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, watermelon
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel
1. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | watermelon | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | gospel     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, pear
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster
1. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
2. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | pear | blueberry |
| Pet    | rabbit    | hamster |

